              novel FFPE-compatible single cell gene expression workflow
              (Chromium Fixed RNA Profiling; scFFPE-seq), spatial
              transcriptomics (Visium CytAssist), and automated
              microscopy-based in situ technology using a 313-plex gene panel
              (Xenium In Situ). Whole transcriptome profiling of the FFPE
              tissue using scFFPE-seq and Visium facilitated the identification
              of 17 different cell types. Xenium allowed us to spatially
